  "comment": "LCB246IP Outdoor LED BAR 24x 6W: The LCB246IP is a durable aluminium LED bar engineered for outdoor environments. Leveraging cutting-edge LED technology, the LCB246IP delivers stunning wash effects. This fixture is versatile, perfect for everything from uplighting expansive venues and buildings to illuminating stages for live events. Featuring a convection-cooled cast aluminium housing, it includes watertight internal gaskets and weather-resistant power and DMX cable in/out connections. Delivery includes an infrared remote control for quick and easy operation.",
